{"query":"query GetAvailableBets($assetToken: Address!, $filterUp: TicketFilter!, $order: [TicketOrder!]!, $page: Page!, $filterDown: TicketFilter!) {
  betsUp: ticketsForToken(
    assetToken: $assetToken
    filter: $filterUp
    order: $order
    page: $page
  ) {
    tickets {
      signature
      maker
      hashVal
      address
      usage
      availableVolume
      assetToken
      payload {
        volume
        nonce
        deadline
        betImplementationAddress
        details {
          isUp
          pool
          strikeUniswapTick
          period
          ratio
          issuerWinFee
          traderWinFee
          exerciseWindowDuration
          claimTo
          __typename
        }
        __typename
      }
      __typename
    }
    totalTickets
    __typename
  }
  betsDown: ticketsForToken(
    assetToken: $assetToken
    filter: $filterDown
    order: $order
    page: $page
  ) {
    tickets {
      signature
      maker
      hashVal
      address
      usage
      availableVolume
      assetToken
      payload {
        volume
        nonce
        deadline
        betImplementationAddress
        details {
          isUp
          pool
          strikeUniswapTick
          period
          ratio
          issuerWinFee
          traderWinFee
          exerciseWindowDuration
          claimTo
          __typename
        }
        __typename
      }
      __typename
    }
    totalTickets
    __typename
  }
}
","operationName":"GetAvailableBets","variables":{"assetToken":"0xc02aaa39b223fe8d0a0e5c4f27ead9083c756cc2","filterUp":{"isUp":true,"availableVolumeMin":"10000000","periodMax":null,"periodMin":null,"strikeUniswapTickMax":null,"strikeUniswapTickMin":null,"ratio":"1","deadlineMin":"1672944489"},"filterDown":{"isUp":false,"availableVolumeMin":"10000000","periodMax":null,"periodMin":null,"strikeUniswapTickMax":null,"strikeUniswapTickMin":null,"ratio":"1","deadlineMin":"1672944489"},"order":{"field":"STRIKE_UNISWAP_TICK","asc":false},"page":{"num":"0","size":"50"}}}
